rticlepaper summarization permalink\" class=\"toc-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Article/Paper Summarization</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/allenai/scholarphi\">allenai/scholarphi: An interactive PDF reader.</a>: paper reading with explanation and definiton</p>\n<ul>\n<li>example: <a href=\"https://s2-reader.apps.allenai.org/?file=https://arxiv.org/pdf/2009.12303v4.pdf\">https://s2-reader.apps.allenai.org/?file=https://arxiv.org/pdf/2009.12303v4.pdf</a></li>\n<li><code>https://s2-reader.apps.allenai.org/?file=%arxivfilepdf</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tldrnow.com/\">TL;DR Now</a>: paper searching and summarization</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"articlepaper-graph-and-relationship\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#articlepaper-graph-and-relationship\" aria-label=\"articlepaper graph and relationship permalink\" class=\"toc-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Article/Paper Graph and Relationship</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.connectedpapers.com/\">Connected Papers</a> : Explore connec